---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="How We Work | Rank4AI" description="No juniors. No handoffs. No layers between you and the work. How Rank4AI delivers AI search visibility for UK businesses.">

<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'About', href: '/about/' },
      { label: 'How We Work' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">How We Work</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">How We Work</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI is not run like a normal agency. There are no juniors, no handoffs, and no layers between you and the people doing the work.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Transparency is non-negotiable. We do not do work you cannot understand. If something does not make sense, we explain it. If there are areas you do not want to focus on, that is fine. We advise, but this is your business.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">This is not static optimisation. AI search systems evolve continuously. Signal weightings shift. Sourcing behaviour changes. Our work is built around research, interpretation and adaptation.</p>

    <h2 class="mb-6">The Process</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6 mb-16">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">1. Audit and agree the scope</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">We run the AI Visibility Audit covering your website, your current AI visibility across all six platforms and your competitor landscape. You see everything before any work starts.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">2. Technical foundations</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">AI crawler access, structured data, Bing submission. Getting this right means everything that follows is attributed correctly from the start.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">3. Site and content</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Architecture, content restructuring, authority content build. Built to the right standard, maintained and extended continuously.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">4. Ecosystem</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Built in parallel with or immediately after the site foundations. The site becomes the canonical source. The ecosystem confirms it across every platform.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">5. Monthly report and action document</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Every month: everything active, AI appearance test results across all six platforms, and your action document covering what we recommend.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">6. Monitoring and correction</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">AI interpretation drifts. We track how AI systems describe your business continuously and correct drift before it becomes a visibility problem.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>


    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/about/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">About Rank4AI</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Services</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-24 px-10">
    <h2 class="mb-4">Get Started</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted mb-10 max-w-[500px] mx-auto">Every engagement begins with the AI Search Visibility Audit.</p>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
